  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Art as a communication tool - imptoving skills of children with disabilities</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Umenie ako n&#xE1;stroj komunik&#xE1;cie &#x2013; zlep&#x161;ovanie postavenia a rozvoj zru&#x10D;nost&#xED; det&#xED; so zdravotn&#xFD;m postihnut&#xED;m</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;The purpose of the project is to improve the status and living conditions of children with disabilities, raising awareness of their rights, introduce new teaching methodologies, artistic skills and educational activities, administrative assistance, cooperation with Slovak volunteers.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;&#xDA;&#x10D;elom projektu je prispie&#x165; k zlep&#x161;eniu postavenia a &#x17E;ivotn&#xFD;ch podmienok det&#xED; so zdravotn&#xFD;m postihnut&#xED;m, zv&#xFD;&#x161;enie povedomia o ich pr&#xE1;vach, predstavi&#x165; nov&#xE9; metodiky v&#xFD;u&#x10D;by, umeleck&#xE9; zru&#x10D;nosti a vzdel&#xE1;vacie aktivity, administrat&#xED;vna v&#xFD;pomoc, spolupr&#xE1;ca so slovensk&#xFD;mi dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;kmi.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
